{"tid":1657172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［核爆］權威民調 65%香港市民支持香港獨立","createTime":"2019-10-16T03:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T14:12:47.000Z","uid":287032,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7a7d805149c976518b3f3b0575db104496eb2d","tid":1657172,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:19:09.000Z","msg":"我朋友係<br />\n中大傳播與民意中心民意調查員<br />\n前星期接左明報job做民意調查<br />\n本來主要問返蒙面法、對政府警隊支持度及最近社會事件（包括開真槍，鶳）既意見同埋評分<br />\n<br />\n但係當中加插左一條問題係問<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你是否支持<span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立</span>？<br />\n1. 支持<br />\n2.反對<br />\n3.無意見</span><br />\n當時平均每10個有6-7個都答<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">支持</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係明報似乎見到呢條題目爭議太大<br />\n亦驚比黨媒追究<br />\n所以無報出黎<br />\n<br />\n已fact check，唔信就請記者直接要求佢公開所有數據"},{"pid":"2ac496c84cf845ce82c11e30906a17e9afd31b04","tid":1657172,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC4rszp.jpg&h=a54a4986&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"27270b6b113b3b09eb23795c872b54457a6a9687","tid":1657172,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:19:49.000Z","msg":"記者快啲追問"},{"pid":"ab25befec0595929477b62304d328b64dec29395","tid":1657172,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:20:31.000Z","msg":"可能政府會全力隱瞞呢件事"},{"pid":"99809b770f5ef426801ef0d715cda98c0699eac7","tid":1657172,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRybVKs25tSz2Dh1RUTKfjAJI7klvqIguEH-defoFWht-YbmHsA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRybVKs25tSz2Dh1RUTKfjAJI7klvqIguEH-def